Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:08.69,BSD - Tea on Rice Narration Font,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,1)}Virus symptoms—{\c&H201361&}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:08.69,sign_2075_2__begin,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,1)}begin
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:22.04,Stray Dogs - Italics,Radio,0000,0000,0000,,The next requested piece is the "Waltz of \Nthe Flowers" from {\i0}The Nutcracker Suite.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:29.25,Stray Dogs - Italics,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Ivan, I've completed the orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:35.13,Stray Dogs - Italics,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ivan, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:36.43,Stray Dogs - Italics,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear Tchaikovsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:44.44,Stray Dogs - Italics,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,Listening to the radio again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:47.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,I infected the intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:50.73,Stray Dogs - Italics,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the boss's next order?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:02.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,Our master instructs you to \Ndo what you can to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:04.83,Stray Dogs - Italics,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,No backup?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:07.04,Stray Dogs - Italics,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,If I get caught, the virus will be lost, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:10.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of protecting \Nanyone other than our master.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:14.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:20.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to see your face the \Nmoment the bliss is gone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:22.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,The skin on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:25.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,If the master were to ask for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:28.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,I would peel it off without \Na second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:31.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,You're completely nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,The bastards are after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:41.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:44.33,sign_4468_24_Episode_37,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 37
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:56.76,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, a connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:58.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.72,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I trust that you're chasing down \Nthe gifted controlling the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:04.35,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,His virus infects the victim \Nthrough open wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:07.14,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The fever and nausea make it \Ndifficult to even just stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:09.77,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let yourselves be so much as grazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.65,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of Fyodor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:15.11,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let that gifted out of your sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I can't reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:35.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Weretiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:41.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Akutagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:47.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,Neither the wretched dog nor the weretiger \Nlive up to their reputations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:51.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:54.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Go faster than him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:56.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you're an uncomfortable ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:02.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:08.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:09.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think. Just run, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You're not paying for this ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:25.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,You're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:29.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Weretiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:36.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:46.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:53.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,My master, Fyodor-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:59.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,has tasked me with something more \Nimportant than guarding him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:59.55,sign_7645_57_Rats_in_the_Hous,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Rats in the House of\N the Dead Agent \NIvan G.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.55,sign_7716_58_Special_Ability_,Special ability,0000,0000,0000,,Special Ability:\NThe Precipice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself, weretiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:07.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to take him down within \Na minute and go after the tram.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:14.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Kenji,0000,0000,0000,,They're on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:17.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai-san, three cars just left the \Nabandoned mines from the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.40,Stray Dogs - Italics,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Contact the surface team and follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:26.07,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Those are decoys meant to slow us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:31.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's what I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.41,Stray Dogs - Italics,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:38.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Kenji,0000,0000,0000,,Tanizaki-san, there's a cargo truck \Nleaving from the west of the mines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:41.59,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore that one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:47.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're seeing several armed \Nsoldiers moving to the southeast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,They're escorting someone in a hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.10,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.02,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We're trying to capture a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We need every hand we can spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:58.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,You're wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,My ability is to control earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:22.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,No amount of cutting or crushing \Nwill defeat my stone giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:28.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Weretiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:37.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that you're\N in the belly of my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:41.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,Even the ground you stand on is your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:48.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed that you survived my blow, \Nman with the ability of the weretiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:54.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there'll be a lot of \Npain to be had before my bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:58.36,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't defeat the stone giant,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.88,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,we have no choice but to go \Nafter the gifted himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.46,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,But if this ground is in the \Nfield of his special ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.30,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,even getting close will be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.13,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Then our only choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Akutagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:12.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you thinking what I'm thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do you think \Nwe've tried to kill each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Stay put, sickly man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:26.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Keep running, fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:28.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:56.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,Is he jumping on the black cloth of that ability \Nto avoid touching the earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:06:59.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell where he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:19.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,An fully-enclosed defense \Nusing fast-spinning rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:23.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't tell where you're coming from,\N I just need to protect myself in all directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:26.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,Now, wretched dog, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:41.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,"Even the ground that you \Nstand on is your enemy."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:46.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid to say, those words have been \Ndirected at my enemies countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:55.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, using me as bait...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:59.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who charged \Nin knowing you were bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:01.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:03.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do you think \Nwe've tried to kill each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go after the tram, weretiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Be my horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, that's—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Weretiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,A golem...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the virus'...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:30.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,My master brings joy to this godless world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:34.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,Evil is the one who stands in his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:38.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,I've infected you with the virus\N through your wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,I have no strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:47.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to go after the tram,\N even if we beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:55.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai-san, there's a helicopter of unknown \Nnationality approaching from the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,We can't fight it off with our equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.31,Stray Dogs - Italics,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Call for the military police to back us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:01.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,A helicopter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone on the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,People?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:10.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Kenji,0000,0000,0000,,There's what appears to be hiker \Nat the base of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:13.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Kenji,0000,0000,0000,,He's wearing a hat, so I can't see his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.03,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:18.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone stop the hiker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:19.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Send Mori-san's men, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:20.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:22.29,Stray Dogs - Italics,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,G-Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai-san, it wasn't him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,He's just an ordinary hiker \Nhandcuffed with grenades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Fyodor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,You two are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:47.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:57.74,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,My body's sinking and I don't \Nhave the strength to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:00.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Weretiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Answer my question from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:11.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,There's a way to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,A last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,But answer me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:22.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:25.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,You know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:29.31,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Principal,0000,0000,0000,,Those who can save no one \Ndo not deserve to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:35.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,You fight to escape your childhood \Nmemories and earn the right to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:39.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard that your childhood master died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,He's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,He's standing behind you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:52.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,He lives in my head now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:57.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,He keeps repeating the cursed words,\N "Do what is right."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:01.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get revenge against \Nsomeone who's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:07.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,That's far more brutal \Nthan my trivial death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:12.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:17.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm a wretched dog, you're a wandering dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,This is the solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:23.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Fight, and give me an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,If you still lose like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:30.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,One of them is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,The whole ground's missing, space and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:52.48,Stray Dogs - Italics,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,Teleportation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.94,Stray Dogs - Italics,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,He carved out space with his ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,and moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,The stone he carved isn't recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:17.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Only those who've tried to kill him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:22.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,know that the tiger's claws can cut \Nthrough the very fabric of an ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:27.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, by expanding and contracting \Nthe space he detached
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:32.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,the same way he cut through my Rashoumon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:39.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,our abilities become a peerless \Nsword against which
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,there can be no defense for \Nphysical armor or abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Akutagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Obliterate him, weretiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Beast Beneath the Moonlight, Rashoumon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Kokuto Zessou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,I made it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:37.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,Fyodor and the Rats in the House of the Dead\N are all tools for my entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:41.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,Weak men like me get away with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:44.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,The haves ought to die barfing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:53.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,See? Just as I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Fukuzawa,0000,0000,0000,,What a simplistic escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:14:00.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Fukuzawa,0000,0000,0000,,Far too predictable compared \Nto Fyodor, master of phantoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:07.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we were all put in mortal \Ndanger because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:08.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0000,0000,0000,,Any thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll disable the virus right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn myself in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:14.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Pushkin,0000,0000,0000,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:18.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Mori,0000,0000,0000,,Good enough, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:18.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Fukuzawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:19.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Fukuzawa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:25.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Fukuzawa,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,The virus is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,The mission was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:43.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0000,0000,0000,,Fyodor's missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,He's nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:52.57,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kunikida,0000,0000,0000,,But he wasn't in the helicopter \Nor the escape vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:56.12,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kunikida,0000,0000,0000,,He must still be in his hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:57.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:04.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:11.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,My master removed the part \Nof me that feels grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:16.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone ever once guarantee that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:18.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,capturing this base would \Nlead you to my master?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:19.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Waiter,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like more tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:30.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Fyodor,0000,0000,0000,,I think not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:31.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Fyodor,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:41.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,He was never even here to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:45.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:48.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,There are no connections \Nto the outside world here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:52.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,We're monitoring cell phone communications \Nwith our hacking ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:56.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,This place can't be operated from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:59.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,It's this music.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:04.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,The requests being made \Non all the music programs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:07.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,are serving as a secret \Nlanguage to relay his orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:12.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,Our communications make use of \Nall the radio waves in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:15.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,No amount of hacking can stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:19.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Ivan,0000,0000,0000,,You'd lost from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.16,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kunikida,0000,0000,0000,,Atsushi, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:24.75,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kunikida,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:30.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,The rat is already outside the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:37.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Fyodor,0000,0000,0000,,The "St. Matthew Passion" by Bach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Fyodor,0000,0000,0000,,It seems my time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:43.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Fyodor,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't nearly as \Nformidable as I'd thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:50.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Fyodor,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I'll be able \Nto end them in my next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:02.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:04.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Nice café, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:11.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen you so shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:17.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You want to ask how \NI found you here, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:21.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I really played my best card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:27.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,This is my best card. \NThe one that caught the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:32.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0000,0000,0000,,Long time, Rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:36.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Fyodor,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Fyodor,0000,0000,0000,,Eyes of God?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:39.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:44.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The inescapable eyes that integrate \Nsurveillance images from all over the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:51.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I used that power to find this place \Nwhile you were distracted by your base.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:55.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He agreed to help us on the \Ncondition that we'd take back
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:58.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,the Guild's hidden assets, \Nwhich you've swiped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:01.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in money \Nonce it's escaped me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:04.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0000,0000,0000,,but my pride wouldn't allow me to \Nleave it in the hands of rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:17.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right, Dazai-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:18.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I called you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0000,0000,0000,,Put your hands where we can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:42.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:48.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0000,0000,0000,,Try anything funny, \Nand we'll shoot you on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Fyodor,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Fyodor,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0000,0000,0000,,Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Francis,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what his ability is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:06.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:24.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Kenji,0000,0000,0000,,It's bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:34.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,We straight-up disobeyed the president's \Norders not to fight against the Port Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,We could be axed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:37.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Kenji,0000,0000,0000,,We could?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:39.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Kenji,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been axed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:40.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what "axed" means?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:44.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:47.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Several people have been \Naxed at my previous job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:49.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Kyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning up after them was such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,This kid doesn't know what \Nthe word means, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:55.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Ranpo,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all these snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:57.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ranpo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:01.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Tanizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You made it out of the mystery novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Ranpo,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:05.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Ranpo,0000,0000,0000,,I identified all 500 criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:07.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Ranpo,0000,0000,0000,,Fancy-hat boy is still inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:11.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Ranpo,0000,0000,0000,,He gave up on the mystery novel \Nand just started beating everyone up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:14.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0000,0000,0000,,It's the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:24.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Kunikida,0000,0000,0000,,We'll accept any punishment in the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:27.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Fukuzawa,0000,0000,0000,,We'll determine your punishment later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:33.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Fukuzawa,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm deeply grateful for \Nyour work on this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:42.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Fukuzawa,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:50.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,This is such a nice venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:52.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:53.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's a beautiful ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Atsushi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:09.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:12.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,How was it working alongside Akutagawa-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:16.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,I never want to partner with him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:18.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,We're just fundamentally incompatible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:25.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,He's short-sighted and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:29.93,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,In six months, I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.64,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Be well-prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:34.80,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,When we first fought on the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:38.32,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,I utterly despised you for \Nhow well-off you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:41.29,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,But that's somewhat different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:45.85,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Until I defeat you, I can't move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:48.87,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:53.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,And what did you tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:57.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:59.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I have a vague idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:01.91,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:04.49,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,But on one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:07.84,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill anyone for the next six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:11.17,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,There's something simple \Nthat you'll learn from that:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.07,0:22:15.18,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,what it takes to win Dazai-san's approval,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:19.55,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,and the fact that weakness and \Nstrength aren't what they seem,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:24.52,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,and that you're really ahead of me already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:29.12,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Akutagawa,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:34.04,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:37.19,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask Kunikida-san to teach me to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:40.38,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll train myself to \Ncontrol my ability better,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.53,0:22:45.85,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,so I can brush off Akutagawa's \Nstrength six months from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:48.03,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,That way,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:51.82,Stray Dogs - Italics,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,I can be freed from the \Nshackles of that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:55.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I figured that's what you'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:03.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,A mafia member who doesn't kill, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.58,0:23:08.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You and Akutagawa-kun are both fighters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.65,0:23:11.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:18.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Atsushi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:23.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,What are we toasting to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:27.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,To the stray dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:33.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Atsushi,0000,0000,0000,,To the stray dogs.
